settings.name: continues
settings.description: Determine the number of continues before hitting Game Over. 21 is unlimited.

settings.name: floppy_req
settings.description: Determines how many Floppy Disks are required.

settings.name: gun_levels
settings.description: Determines Zillion gun power for the number of Zillion power ups you pick up.

values.name: restrictive
values.description: Champ is the only one that can get Zillion gun power level 3.

settings.name: jump_levels
settings.description: Determines jump levels for each character level.

values.name: restrictive
values.description: Apple is the only one that can get jump level 3.

settings.name: randomize_alarms
settings.description: Whether to randomize the locations of alarm sensors.

settings.name: opas_per_level
settings.description: Determines how many Opa-Opas required to level up.

settings.name: id_card_count
settings.description: Determines how many ID cards are in the game. *(Vanilla is 63)*

settings.name: bread_count
settings.description: Determines how many Bread are in the game. *(Vanilla is 33)*

settings.name: opa_opa_count
settings.description: Determines how many Opa-Opas are in the game. *(Vanilla is 26)*

settings.name: zillion_count
settings.description: Determines how many Zillion gun power ups are in the game. *(Vanilla is 6)

settings.name: floppy_disk_count
settings.description: Determines how many Floppy Disks are in the game. *(Vanilla is 5)*

settings.name: scope_count
settings.description: Determines how many Scopes are in the game. *(Vanilla is 4)*

settings.name: red_id_card_count
settings.description: Determines how many Red ID Cards are in the game. *(Vanilla is 1)*

settings.name: skill
settings.description: The difficulty level of the game. The higher the number, the harder the game.

settings.name: starting_cards
settings.description: Determines how many ID Cards to start the game with.

settings.name: room_gen
settings.description: Whether to generate rooms with random terrain.
